# 📝 To-Do App (Flask)

A simple, clean, and secure To-Do app built with Flask.  
Features user registration, login, per-user tasks, task status tracking, profile display, and modern UI.

## 🚀 Features

- **User Registration & Login** (passwords securely hashed)
- **Add, Toggle, Delete & Clear Tasks:**  
  - Each user sees only their own tasks (tasks are private)
  - Tasks support status cycling: Pending → Working → Done
  - Delete individual tasks or clear all at once
- **Profile page:**  
  - Displays your username and profile avatar (initial-based)
  - Accessible via the header icon
- **Beautiful UI:** Responsive, clean navigation & design
- **Session-based Authentication**

